# Privacy Policy for Calculator App

**Effective Date:** November 2, 2025  
**Last Updated:** November 2, 2025

## Introduction

Thank you for using Calculator App ("we," "our," or "the App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our calculator application on Android devices.

## Information We Collect

### Information We Collect Directly

Our Calculator App is designed with your privacy in mind. We **DO NOT** directly collect, store, or transmit:

- Personal identification information (name, email, phone number, etc.)
- Calculation history or data
- Location data

### Information Collected by Third-Party Services

Our app displays advertisements through third-party advertising partners. These partners may automatically collect certain information to provide personalized ads and improve their services:

**Google AdMob (or your ad network) may collect:**
- Advertising ID (a unique, user-resettable ID for advertising)
- Device information (device model, operating system version)
- IP address (approximate location)
- App usage data and interactions with ads
- Technical information (screen size, language settings)

**Note:** You can opt-out of personalized advertising by:
- Going to your device Settings → Google → Ads → Opt out of Ads Personalization
- Or using your device's advertising ID reset feature

### Permissions

Our app may request the following permissions:

- **INTERNET** - Required to display advertisements
- **ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE** - To check internet connectivity for ads

## How We Use Information

We do not directly use any personal information. However, our third-party advertising partners use the information they collect to:

- Display relevant advertisements
- Measure ad performance and engagement
- Prevent fraud and improve ad quality
- Provide analytics to advertisers

All advertising data is processed by our advertising partners according to their own privacy policies.

## Data Storage

All calculations performed in the app are processed locally on your device and are **not stored** permanently. When you close the app, calculation history (if displayed during the session) is automatically cleared.

## Third-Party Services

Our Calculator App integrates with the following third-party services:

### Advertising Networks

We use **Google AdMob** (or specify your ad network) to display advertisements. AdMob may use cookies and similar technologies to collect information for ad personalization and measurement.

**AdMob Privacy Policy:** https://policies.google.com/privacy  
**AdMob Partners:** https://support.google.com/admob/answer/9012903

### Other Third-Party Services

Our app does **not** integrate with:
- Analytics services beyond what's provided by ad networks
- Social media platforms
- Cloud storage services

**Important:** We do not control and are not responsible for the privacy practices of third-party advertising networks. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.

## Children's Privacy

Our app is suitable for users of all ages. However, we are committed to protecting children's privacy:

- We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13
- Our advertising partners comply with COPPA (Children's Online Privacy Protection Act)
- Ads shown to children are non-personalized and age-appropriate

**For parents:** If you believe your child has provided personal information through our app, please contact us immediately, and we will work to have it removed.

## Data Security

Since no data is collected or transmitted from your device, there are no security concerns related to data breaches or unauthorized access to your information.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.

## Your Rights

Since we do not collect any personal data, there is no user data to access, modify, or delete.

## International Users

This app can be used globally. As we do not collect any data, international data transfer regulations do not apply.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

**Email:** [your-email@example.com]  
**Developer:** [Your Name/Company Name]

## Consent

By using our Calculator App, you consent to this Privacy Policy.

---

**Summary:** This calculator app respects your privacy completely. We do not collect, store, share, or transmit any of your data. All calculations are performed locally on your device.
